{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──開業して2週目の朝。\nポストに無言で差し込まれた請求書の束を見て、俺は目眩がした。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（電気代、水道代、家賃...やばい、金がない...）"
    },
    {
      "include": "common/weekly_settlement"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（所持金は残り少ない…。客は未だにタツ姐だけ。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（でも、利子の猶予があるだけマシか...タツ姐には感謝しないと。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（……って、感謝する相手が闇金ってどうなんだ...）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "おう。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "タツ姐さん！来てくれたんですね！"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "...まぁ、確かに効いたからな。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "先週の施術の後、肩が軽くなった気がする。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "本当ですか！それは良かった！"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "調子に乗るなよ。借金は借金だからな。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "わ、わかってます...。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（でも、効果を認めてくれたのは嬉しいな...）"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "おかげで麻雀で3半荘打てたからな。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "それはすごいですね！"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "で、今日はどうすんだ？",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "今日は背中と腰を中心に施術しようと思います。"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "背中と腰か。確かに、そこも凝ってんだよな。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "うつ伏せの姿勢で施術させていただきます。"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "うつ伏せ？まぁ、そういうもんか。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "はい。背中から腰にかけて、しっかりほぐしていきますね。"
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_massage2",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "背中と腰の状態を確認してもいいですか？",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "背筋の張りを確認する",
          "trustDelta": 2,
          "developDelta": 0,
          "next": "normal_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "いいケツしてますね",
          "trustDelta": 0,
          "developDelta": 1,
          "next": "nice_butt_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "尻を揉む",
          "trustDelta": 0,
          "developDelta": 2,
          "next": "butt_grab_path"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "normal_path",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "背筋がかなり張ってますね。深層筋をゆっくり緩めていきます。"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "…まぁ、真面目にやってるうちは許す。",
      "outfit": "suit",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "nice_butt_path",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "（うつ伏せのタツ姐の後ろ姿に、つい本音が漏れる…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "タツ姐さん…いいケツしてますね。"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "…は？今なんつった？",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "い、いや！整体師的な意味で！筋肉のバランスがすごくいいなって…！"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "……テメェ、それ施術中に言うセリフじゃねぇだろ。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "す、すみません…！"
    },
    {
      "character": "タツ姐",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "…ったく。次言ったら利子上乗せすっからな。",
      "outfit": "suit",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "butt_grab_path",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "大臀筋の張りを確認しますね…"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
